data.description: Gorgeous newly remodeled home located in the charming, 55+ Desert Inn Mobile community. Step into an open floor plan featuring wood look porcelain tile floors throughout, new windows and custom wood shutters, a gourmet kitchen with stunning granite counters, high end appliances, custom cabinets with pull out drawers, and leather granite backsplash behind the stove. Primary suite offers a massive walk-in closet, additional storage in the primary bathroom with a large walk-in shower. Enjoy a serene backyard with low maintenance astro-turf, and a large patio cover, and covered deck perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee or a good book. A perfect place to entertain or relax. Home also comes with a soft water system, a new roof (less than 1 year old) and a Tuff Shed.. Book a showing today!
